{"tid":1809425,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警察偵緝訓練中心外水馬寫「畜牲」 廚師認刑毀罰 2000 元","createTime":"2020-01-03T05:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T05:50:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a0647cf0f5eb0adf622ba75000e0237e1a68fa","tid":1809425,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"中年男廚師上月於葵涌的警察偵緝訓練中心外，在水馬寫上「畜牲」二字，被巡邏警當場截獲及拘捕，廚師今（3 日）於西九龍裁判法院承認刑毀罪。辯方求情指他一時衝動「想唔開」，終被判罰款 2000 元，及賠償香港政府 277 元清潔費。被告在庭外稱，因近數月於電視見盡警方濫權，認為警方十分暴力、殘忍，衰過大陸公安，才會寫上「畜牲」二字。<br />\n<br />\n被告黃國杰（43 歲，廚師）今承認一項刑事毀壞罪，控罪指被告於去年 12 月 11 日，在葵涌和宜合道 302 號警察偵緝訓練中心外，無合法辯解損毀一個水馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%81%B5%E7%B7%9D%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E6%B0%B4%E9%A6%AC%E5%AF%AB-%E7%95%9C%E7%89%B2-%E5%BB%9A%E5%B8%AB%E8%AA%8D%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E7%BD%B0-2000-%E5%85%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2581%25B5%25E7%25B7%259D%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25AF%25AB-%25E7%2595%259C%25E7%2589%25B2-%25E5%25BB%259A%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E7%25BD%25B0-2000-%25E5%2585%2583%2F&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7ElZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=0f8e4c50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2581%25B5%25E7%25B7%259D%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25AF%25AB-%25E7%2595%259C%25E7%2589%25B2-%25E5%25BB%259A%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E7%25BD%25B0-2000-%25E5%2585%2583%2F&h=ede77b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%81%B5%E7%B7%9D%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E6%B0%B4%E9%A6%AC%E5%AF%AB-%E7%9